{
  "stem": "21437.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to go-- I was there every day because I had to go to-- to my school next to it, that was next with the shul.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was only this one synagogue, and it was on-- on the other end of the town on the left hand side, which was quite far to go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went very often when I went with my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Friday night, Saturday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was coming-- I suppose that was-- that was one of the reasons why we shifted so he could come and say [HEBREW], you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- in the morning, I watched him quite often.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if he made sure that I watch him, or it just happened like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know that I watched him with reverence, you know, and he was putting on-- on the tefillin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when he was, you know, putting on the band and putting on the tallit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was such a ritual.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That I could see although it-- it repeated itself every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I could see that he was focusing whilst he was putting it on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think everything else fell away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was-- he was really praying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was really doing it from-- from his heart, with his heart and with his mind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is, I suppose, where my perception came where-- if-- whatever you do, you've got to do your best and you've got to do from your heart.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Just do it with your head is not good enough.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this is what I perceived when he was putting on that tefillin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when my mother was lighting the candles, it was the same thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
